            . I keep a broker's shop, in Upper Rosoman-street. On the 19th of April the prisoner came and offered a shovel and a pair of tongs for sale - I asked what had become of the poker; she said,"Me and him (I suppose she meant her husband) have had some words, and he threw it out of the window;" I said I thought they were not hers - she said if I would give them to her she would fetch the person; I said, No, I would detain them, and she might go for the person - she went out very quick; I thought it was not all right, and I took them to the Police-constable.</p>
